[27/03/2019 00:32:37] <font color="#ffffff">No quiere sentir nada.</font>
[27/03/2019 00:32:39] <font color="#ffffff">Totalmente comprensible.</font>
[27/03/2019 00:32:40] <font color="#ffffff">Vale.</font>
