[27/03/2019 23:16:09] <font color="#00ff00">estaba tremendamente</font>
[27/03/2019 23:16:12] <font color="#00ff00">delgado, pálido.</font>
[27/03/2019 23:16:15] <font color="#00ff00">Al pobre le resbalaban</font>
[27/03/2019 23:16:15] <font color="#00ff00">las lágrimas de los ojos</font>
[27/03/2019 23:16:17] <font color="#00ff00">y no podía contenerlas.</font>
